data.description: GULF FRONT COMPLEX!  This is your opportunity to transform a 2 bedroom 2 bathroom condo with limited Intracoastal water views and in need of updating into your very own slice of Paradise. Why wait and pay extra for someone else's updates when you can do it exactly the way you want it? Brand new A/C and newer hot water heater. Complex pool and re-nourished beach are just steps away from each other.  This property also offers a BBQ area and two large boardwalk-type lounge areas to soak up the sun while watching beautiful views of the gulf or amazing sunsets.
